author: Sukriti Gumber
title: Are These Ye Hai Mohabbatein Actors Dating Each Other?
text:
A post shared by Work💋dance💋shop💋travel💋party (@krishna_mukherjee786) on Jan 14, 2017 at 5:50am PST 
Buzz was strong that Aly Goni , who plays Romi in Ye Hai Mohabbatein is dating Krishna Mukherjee , who plays Aaliya in the same show. The rumours died a natural death eventually, until recently when Aly and Krishna’s alleged closeness again came to the fore. 
Aly celebrated his birthday a couple of days ago, and Krishna posted this really hot photo of them posing in front of the mirror. Check it out: A post shared by Work💋dance💋shop💋travel💋party (@krishna_mukherjee786) on Feb 25, 2017 at 5:39am PST Further, Aly’s parents came down to meet him for his birthday, and Aaliya was also present for the family reunion: ❤❤ A post shared by The Aly Goni (@alygoni) on Feb 25, 2017 at 6:40am PST Aly also threw a birthday party for his friends – and no points for guessing – Krishna was present at the bash: A post shared by The Aly Goni (@alygoni) on Feb 26, 2017 at 3:15am PST 
Ahem… what’s brewing, guys? Although the two often refer to each other as their best friend in their social media posts, one can’t deny that they make a hella good – looking couple. Do you agree? 3
